Package Coords

Interface coords_converter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MyCoords
    public interface coords_converter
    This interface represents a basic coordinate system converter, including: 1. The 3D vector between two lat,lon, alt points 2. Adding a 3D vector in meters to a global point. 3. convert a 3D vector from meters to polar coordinates
    Author:
    Boaz Ben-Moshe
